  <Subject Subject_ID="300034063">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300034017</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>orthographic projections (images) [300034017], images by method of projection [300068504], images by method of representation [300033974], visual works by form of image [300191088], visual works by form [300191087], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to drawings or works in another two-dimensional medium where the work is created using multiview projection, which is a system of projection in which principal faces of an object or structure are parallel to the picture plane, but multiple views of the object or structure are provided in order to fully represent all sides of it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a dibujos creados usando proyección de múltiples puntos de vista, que es un sistema de proyección en que las caras principales de un objeto o estructura están paralelos al plano de la imagen, pero que se proveen puntos de vista múltiple de manera de representar la totalidad de todos sus lados.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar tekeningen gemaakt aan de hand van multiview-projectie, een projectie waarbij de belangrijkste zijden van een object of structuur parallel zijn aan het beeldvlak, maar waarbij op meerdere aanzichten van het object of de structuur alle kanten ervan volledig worden weergegeven.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指運用多面投影創作的製圖或其他媒材的平面作品，即物件或結構物的主要平面與繪畫平面平行的投影系統，並呈現該物件或結構物的多個視面，以展現其全面性。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Beschreibt eine Zeichnung oder eine Arbeit in einem anderen zweidimensionalen Medium, in der die Arbeit in Normalprojektion, einem Projektionssystem, bei dem die Hauptansichten eines Objekts oder einer Struktur parallel zur Darstellungsebene sind, aber verschiedene Ansichten des Objekts oder der Struktur geboten werden, um alle Seiten darzustellen, angefertigt wurde.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refere-se aos desenhos ou trabalhos em um outro meio bidimensional nos quais o trabalho é criado usando projeções com vistas múltiplas, isto é, um sistema de projeção no qual as faces principais de um objeto ou estrutura estão paralelas ao plano da imagem, mas as vistas múltiplas do objeto ou da estrutura são fornecidas com o objetivo de representar completamente todos os seus lados.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000179/VP-intern</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000110648/Portuguese Translation Intern Project (2020-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
